metadata.name: WE 1
metadata.description:
“WE” it’s a collection to celebrate diversity and uniqueness of each human being. We are all different and that is what makes us so beautiful and special.  It’s the differences that make us grow as species, even with all the obstacles and challenges.  
This collection is minted across several blockchains and platforms, so the collector and viewer can also have that freedom of choice and celebrate decentralization.  
Each piece is minted only on one platform and chain.   All the pieces on this collection are free to be used and adapted as you wish. You can create derivative pieces, print them, make your own art with it, use it as pfp, etc. Freedom and choice to all. 

Created initially by Magusz.  #love #empathy #diversity #inclusion #decentralization #empowered   #magusz #art #uniqueness
